    "description": {
      "value": "\n<p><b>Type:</b> Ninjutsu (Suiton)</p>\n<p><b>Rank:</b> 7 (Spell Level 4)</p>\n<p><b>Chakra Cost:</b> 7</p>\n\n<p><b>Learn DC:</b> 21 | <b>Successes:</b> 4</p>\n<p><b>Perform:</b> 9 | <b>Perform DC:</b> 22</p>\n\n<p><b>Components:</b> C, H</p>\n\n<hr>\n\n<p>Rainfall within the area turns to iron for a short time, dealing 6d8 damage to all creatures and structures in the area (if there is no rain, nothing happens). Structures cannot make a save for half damage, and they take double damage if their entire width is encompassed by the area.</p>\n\n\n\n",
